      {
        "body": [
          {
            "body": [
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "value": "The fire confirms it. This is no trinket, Frodo. It is the\nEnemy's own — and while it rests in the Shire, the Shire is\nin peril."
                  }
                ],
                "kind": "paragraph"
              }
            ],
            "closeStyle": "named",
            "inline": false,
            "kind": "nodeUse",
            "name": "say",
            "params": [
              {
                "name": "who",
                "value": "Gandalf"
              },
              {
                "name": "mood",
                "value": "grave"
              }
            ],
            "paramsSource": "pipes"
          },
          {
            "body": [
              {
                "inline": false,
                "kind": "comment",
                "text": "branch: offer it away"
              },
              {
                "body": [
                  {
                    "body": [
                      {
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "kind": "text",
                            "value": "Then you take it. You're wise, you're strong. Keep it hidden."
                          }
                        ],
                        "kind": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    "closeStyle": "named",
                    "inline": false,
                    "kind": "nodeUse",
                    "name": "say",
                    "params": [
                      {
                        "name": "who",
                        "value": "Frodo"
                      },
                      {
                        "name": "mood",
                        "value": "afraid"
                      }
                    ],
                    "paramsSource": "pipes"
                  },
                  {
                    "body": [
                      {
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "kind": "text",
                            "value": "Do not offer it to me. I dare not so much as hold it. The Ring\nwould find the good in me and turn it to ruin."
                          }
                        ],
                        "kind": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    "closeStyle": "named",
                    "inline": false,
                    "kind": "nodeUse",
                    "name": "say",
                    "params": [
                      {
                        "name": "who",
                        "value": "Gandalf"
                      },
                      {
                        "name": "mood",
                        "value": "urgent"
                      }
                    ],
                    "paramsSource": "pipes"
                  },
                  {
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "body": null,
                        "closeStyle": "parens",
                        "inline": false,
                        "kind": "nodeUse",
                        "name": "goto",
                        "params": [
                          {
                            "name": "scene",
                            "value": "what-must-be-done"
                          }
                        ],
                        "paramsSource": "pipes"
                      }
                    ],
                    "kind": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "closeStyle": "named",
                "inline": false,
                "kind": "nodeUse",
                "name": "choice",
                "params": [],
                "paramsSource": "none"
              },
              {
                "inline": false,
                "kind": "comment",
                "text": "branch: ask why"
              },
              {
                "body": [
                  {
                    "body": [
                      {
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "kind": "text",
                            "value": "But why me? I'm no one — a hobbit who's never been past Bree."
                          }
                        ],
                        "kind": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    "closeStyle": "named",
                    "inline": false,
                    "kind": "nodeUse",
                    "name": "say",
                    "params": [
                      {
                        "name": "who",
                        "value": "Frodo"
                      },
                      {
                        "name": "mood",
                        "value": "lost"
                      }
                    ],
                    "paramsSource": "pipes"
                  },
                  {
                    "body": [
                      {
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "kind": "text",
                            "value": "Small hands turn the wheel of the world while the eyes of the\ngreat look elsewhere. It fell to you. That is reason enough."
                          }
                        ],
                        "kind": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    "closeStyle": "named",
                    "inline": false,
                    "kind": "nodeUse",
                    "name": "say",
                    "params": [
                      {
                        "name": "who",
                        "value": "Gandalf"
                      },
                      {
                        "name": "mood",
                        "value": "gentle"
                      }
                    ],
                    "paramsSource": "pipes"
                  },
                  {
                    "body": [
                      {
                        "body": [
                          {
                            "body": [
                              {
                                "children": [
                                  {
                                    "kind": "text",
                                    "value": "Then I'll carry it. Wherever it must go."
                                  }
                                ],
                                "kind": "paragraph"
                              }
                            ],
                            "closeStyle": "named",
                            "inline": false,
                            "kind": "nodeUse",
                            "name": "say",
                            "params": [
                              {
                                "name": "who",
                                "value": "Frodo"
                              },
                              {
                                "name": "mood",
                                "value": "resolved"
                              }
